OL,5,CAmazon staff
OL,6, The trade union Unite is setting up a
OL,7, hotline for Amazon staff to complain
OL,8, about their treatment at work.
OL,10,FOrganiser Sharon Graham told the BBC it
OL,11,Fwas time the internet retail giant
OL,12,Fshared its "bonanza profits with the
OL,13,Fworkers who help make them".
OL,15,FAmazon had its most lucrative year ever
OL,16,Fin 2020, helped by a surge in online
OL,17,Fshopping during the pandemic.
OL,19,FThe company said it offered its staff
OL,20,F"excellent" pay, benefits and career
OL,21,Fopportunities, plus "safe" conditions.
